#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.cumsum"
msgstr "# triton.language.cumsum"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:4
msgid "简介：`triton.language.cumsum` 计算输入tensor沿指定轴的累积和，返回累积求和结果。"
msgstr "Description: `triton.language.cumsum` computes the cumulative sum of the input tensor along the specified axis and returns the cumulative summation result."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.cumsum(input, axis=0, reverse=False)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | 输入tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | 沿着哪个维度进行累积和操作，默认为0 |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | 如果为True，沿反方向进行累积和操作 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type | Description |\n"
"|-----------|------|-------------|\n"
"| `input` | `Tensor` | Input tensor |\n"
"| `axis` | `int` | The dimension along which to compute the cumulative sum, default is 0 |\n"
"| `reverse` | `bool` | If True, performs the cumulative sum in reverse direction |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:14
msgid "`cumsum` 函数计算沿指定轴的累积和（前缀和）。例如，对于输入 `[a, b, c, d]`，累积和结果为 `[a, a+b, a+b+c, a+b+c+d]`。"
msgstr "The `cumsum` function computes the cumulative sum (prefix sum) along a specified axis. For example, for the input `[a, b, c, d]`, the cumulative sum result is `[a, a+b, a+b+c, a+b+c+d]`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:16
msgid "当 `reverse=True` 时，计算反向累积和：`[a+b+c+d, b+c+d, c+d, d]`。"
msgstr "When `reverse=True`, the reverse cumulative sum is computed: `[a+b+c+d, b+c+d, c+d, d]`."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Scan_Sort_Ops/cumsum.md:18
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor`：计算输入tensor沿指定轴的累积和，返回累积求和结果。\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor`: Computes the cumulative sum of the input tensor along the specified axis, returning the cumulative summation result.\n"

